    data: '{"type":"planner-step","data":{"tag_type":"planner_step","timestamp":"2025-10-14T15:26:28.505400+00:00","step_number":2,"content":"Step 1. (Preparation â€“ Approval of BPT)\\n\\nâ€¢â€‚Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢â€‚Action: Approve the VotingEscrow contract to spend BPT tokens.  \\nâ€¢â€‚Arguments:  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: Use the MockBPT deployed address (\\"0x5FbDB2315678afecb367f032d93F642f64180aa3\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"approve\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [VotingEscrow contract address (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\"), approvalAmount]  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒ(Note: Choose an approvalAmount large enough to cover the locks you plan to create.)  \\nâ€¢â€‚Rationale: The hypothesis requires that the VotingEscrow contract be able to pull BPT (the underlying asset for locks) so that new locks (including dust locks) can be created.\\n\\nâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€"},"tag_type":"PLANNER_STEP","stream_id":"stream_102","stream_complete":true}',
