    opcode: 1,
    data: '{"type":"planner-step","data":{"tag_type":"planner_step","timestamp":"2025-10-14T15:26:28.505426+00:00","step_number":3,"content":"Step 2. (Establish the Baseline)\\n\\nA. Create an initial (baseline) lock â€“ â€œprevious token.â€\\n\\nâ€¢â€‚Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢â€‚Action: Call VotingEscrow.createLock to create a new lock that mints a veNFT.  \\nâ€¢â€‚Arguments:  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: VotingEscrow (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"createLock\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [initialAmount, lockDuration, maxLockEnabled]  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒFor example: initialAmount = 10Ã—10^18 (10 tokens, assuming 18 decimals),  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒlockDuration = a number of seconds (e.g. 365 days in seconds),  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒmaxLockEnabled = false  \\nâ€¢â€‚Rationale: This lock produces the first â€œprevious tokenâ€â€”its veNFT ID (say tokenId_baseline) will be used to start the testing sequence. Save its returned token ID.\\n\\nB. Reset the baseline token to accrue its initial unclaimedFlux.\\n\\nâ€¢â€‚Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢â€‚Action: Call Voter.reset using the baseline token.  \\nâ€¢â€‚Arguments:  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: Voter (\\"0x2279B7A0a67DB372996a5FaB50D91eAA73d2eBe6\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"reset\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [tokenId_baseline]  \\nâ€¢â€‚Rationale: The reset call (after the new epoch, enforced by the onlyNewEpoch modifier) will trigger the VotingEscrow.abstain call and then IFluxToken(FLUX).accrueFlux(_tokenId) so that FluxTokenâ€™s unclaimedFlux for the baseline token gets set.  \\n \\nC. Read and store the baseline unclaimedFlux value.\\n\\nâ€¢â€‚Tool: call_view_tool  \\nâ€¢â€‚Action: Query FluxToken.getUnclaimedFlux for the baseline token.  \\nâ€¢â€‚Arguments:  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: FluxToken (\\"0x0165878A594ca255338adfa4d48449f69242Eb8F\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"getUnclaimedFlux\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [tokenId_baseline]  \\nâ€¢â€‚Rationale: This recorded baseline amount (call it flux_baseline) will be our benchmark for later comparisons.\\n\\nâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€"},"tag_type":"PLANNER_STEP","stream_id":"stream_103","stream_complete":true}',
