    opcode: 1,
    data: '{"type":"planner-step","data":{"tag_type":"planner_step","timestamp":"2025-10-14T15:27:34.624048+00:00","step_number":2,"content":"Step 1. (Preparation â€“ Approval of BPT)\\n\\nâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢ Action: Approve the VotingEscrow contract (address: \\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\") to spend BPT.  \\nâ€¢ Arguments:  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: \\"0x5FbDB2315678afecb367f032d93F642f64180aa3\\" (MockBPT)  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"approve\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [ \\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\", approvalAmount ]  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒ(e.g. approvalAmount = 100e18 wei; adjust per your testing needs)  \\nâ€¢ Rationale: This ensures VotingEscrow can pull BPT tokens needed for lock creation.\\n\\nâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€"},"tag_type":"PLANNER_STEP","stream_id":"stream_122","stream_complete":true}',
