    data: '{"type":"planner-step","data":{"tag_type":"planner_step","timestamp":"2025-10-14T15:28:35.498728+00:00","step_number":7,"content":"Step 4. (Iterative Merging Loop â€“ 10 Iterations)\\n\\nFor each iteration i from 1 to 10, do the following:\\n\\nA. Create a new â€œdustâ€ lock (new token).\\n\\nâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢ Action: Call VotingEscrow.createLock\\nâ€¢ Arguments:\\nâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: VotingEscrow (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\")\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"createLock\\"\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [ dustAmount, shortLockDuration, maxLockEnabled ]\\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒ(e.g., dustAmount = minimal accepted amount such as 1 wei; shortLockDuration = set to a period ensuring the lock will not expireâ€”ensure valid input, maxLockEnabled = false)\\nâ€¢ Rationale: This mints a new veNFT (newTokenId) that will be used as the merge target.\\n\\nB. Merge the previous token into the new token.\\n\\nâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢ Action: Call VotingEscrow.merge\\nâ€¢ Arguments:\\nâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: VotingEscrow (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\")\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"merge\\"\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [ prevTokenId, newTokenId ]\\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒFor the first iteration, prevTokenId is tokenId_baseline; for later iterations, use the newTokenId from the previous iteration.\\nâ€¢ Rationale: This triggers IFluxToken(FLUX).mergeFlux transferring unclaimedFlux from the source to the new token and resetting the sourceâ€™s flux.\\n\\nC. Reset the new token.\\n\\nâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€¢ Action: Call Voter.reset\\nâ€¢ Arguments:\\nâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: Voter (\\"0x2279B7A0a67DB372996a5FaB50D91eAA73d2eBe6\\")\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"reset\\"\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [ newTokenId ]\\nâ€¢ Rationale: This causes accrual (via IFluxToken(FLUX).accrueFlux(newTokenId)) so that the new tokenâ€™s unclaimedFlux increases.\\n\\nD. Query and record the unclaimedFlux for the new token.\\n\\nâ€¢ Tool: call_view_tool  \\nâ€¢ Action: Query FluxToken.getUnclaimedFlux\\nâ€¢ Arguments:\\nâ€ƒâ€“ contract_address: FluxToken (\\"0x0165878A594ca255338adfa4d48449f69242Eb8F\\")\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_name: \\"getUnclaimedFlux\\"\\nâ€ƒâ€“ function_args: [ newTokenId ]\\nâ€¢ Rationale: Ensure the flux value strictly increases relative to the previous tokenâ€™s flux; then set prevTokenId = newTokenId for next iteration.\\n\\nâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€"},"tag_type":"PLANNER_STEP","stream_id":"stream_143","stream_complete":true}',
