    data: '{"type":"planner-step","data":{"tag_type":"planner_step","timestamp":"2025-10-14T15:29:46.669165+00:00","step_number":7,"content":"Step 3. Iterative Merging Loop (10 Iterations)\\n\\nFor each iteration i = 1 to 10:\\n\\nA. Create a â€œDustâ€ Lock  \\nâ€ƒâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒAction: Call VotingEscrow.createLock.  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Contract Address: VotingEscrow (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Function: \\"createLock\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Arguments: [ dustAmount, shortLockDuration, maxLockEnabled ]\\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒExample: dustAmount = minimal value (e.g. 1 wei), shortLockDuration = valid duration ensuring the lock remains active, maxLockEnabled = false.  \\nâ€ƒRationale: This mints a new dust veNFT; record its token id as newTokenId.\\n\\nB. Merge Previous Token into the New Token  \\nâ€ƒâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒAction: Call VotingEscrow.merge.  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Contract Address: VotingEscrow (\\"0xa513E6E4b8f2a923D98304ec87F64353C4D5C853\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Function: \\"merge\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Arguments: [ prevTokenId, newTokenId ]\\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€ƒFor the first iteration, prevTokenId = tokenId_baseline; update prevTokenId each time.  \\nâ€ƒRationale: This will internally call IFluxToken(FLUX).mergeFlux to transfer unclaimedFlux from the source to the new token (and zero out the source).\\n\\nC. Reset the New Token  \\nâ€ƒâ€¢ Tool: send_transaction_tool  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒAction: Call Voter.reset.  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Contract Address: Voter (\\"0x2279B7A0a67DB372996a5FaB50D91eAA73d2eBe6\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Function: \\"reset\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Arguments: [ newTokenId ]  \\nâ€ƒRationale: This triggers an accrual of unclaimedFlux on the new token via IFluxToken(FLUX).accrueFlux.\\n\\nD. Record and Verify unclaimedFlux  \\nâ€ƒâ€¢ Tool: call_view_tool  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒAction: Query FluxToken.getUnclaimedFlux.  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Contract Address: FluxToken (\\"0x0165878A594ca255338adfa4d48449f69242Eb8F\\")  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Function: \\"getUnclaimedFlux\\"  \\nâ€ƒâ€ƒâ€“ Arguments: [ newTokenId ]  \\nâ€ƒRationale: Confirm that the new tokenâ€™s flux is strictly greater than that of the previous token. Save this value and update prevTokenId = newTokenId for the next iteration.\\n\\nâ”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€â”€"},"tag_type":"PLANNER_STEP","stream_id":"stream_179","stream_complete":true}',
